short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds ColorFlip and AutoStrobe for Square Games by Jonas Bo on fxhash.xyz

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Adds some features to tokens of "Square Games" by Jonas Bo on fxhash:

Press 'x' to trigger ColorFlip.
Press 'a' to toggle AutoStrobe.
While AutoStrobe is active, press 'x' to change strobe interval.
Only works in presentation mode.

Find the original Square Games tokens on fxhash.xyz
